{"prompt": "Generate a clean website for an accounting services firm. The brand color should be a sophisticated charcoal grey.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Apex Accounting Solutions</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --primary-color: #36454F; /* Charcoal Grey */\n            --secondary-color: #5A6A75;\n            --accent-color: #D3D3D3;\n            --text-color: #f0f0f0;\n            --dark-text-color: #212121;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            scroll-behavior: smooth;\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            padding: 40px 0;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            border-bottom: 3px solid var(--secondary-color);\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 2.8em;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n        }\n\n        header p {\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n        }\n\n        nav {\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            padding: 15px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n        }\n\n        nav a {\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-decoration: none;\n            margin: 0 20px;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        nav a:hover {\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n        }\n\n        section {\n            padding: 60px 0;\n        }\n\n        #hero {\n            background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--primary-color), var(--secondary-color));\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 100px 0;\n            position: relative;\n        }\n\n        #hero h2 {\n            font-size: 3em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            letter-spacing: 1px;\n        }\n\n        #hero p {\n            font-size: 1.4em;\n            max-width: 700px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n        }\n\n        .section-title {\n            text-align: center;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 40px;\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n            letter-spacing: 1px;\n        }\n\n        .services-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));\n            gap: 30px;\n        }\n\n        .service-item {\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            padding: 30px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, background-color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .service-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            background-color: #40505C;\n        }\n\n        .service-item i {\n            font-size: 3em;\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n\n        .service-item h3 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            font-size: 1.6em;\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n        }\n\n        .service-item p {\n            font-size: 1em;\n        }\n\n        #about {\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            color: var(--dark-text-color);\n        }\n\n        #about h2 {\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n        }\n\n        #contact {\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        #contact p {\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form {\n            max-width: 600px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            padding: 30px;\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n        }\n\n        .contact-form input,\n        .contact-form textarea {\n            width: calc(100% - 20px);\n            padding: 12px;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            border: 1px solid var(--accent-color);\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            font-size: 1em;\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n        }\n\n        .contact-form textarea {\n            height: 150px;\n            resize: vertical;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form button {\n            background-color: var(--accent-color);\n            color: var(--dark-text-color);\n            padding: 15px 30px;\n            border: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form button:hover {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 30px 0;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n        }\n    </style>\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css\">\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h1>Apex Accounting Solutions</h1>\n            <p>Your Trusted Partner in Financial Clarity</p>\n        </div>\n    </header>\n\n    <nav>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <a href=\"#services\">Services</a>\n            <a href=\"#about\">About Us</a>\n            <a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a>\n        </div>\n    </nav>\n\n    <section id=\"hero\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Navigate Your Finances with Confidence</h2>\n            <p>We provide comprehensive accounting services to help your business thrive.</p>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"services\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2 class=\"section-title\">Our Services</h2>\n            <div class=\"services-grid\">\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-chart-line\"></i>\n                    <h3>Bookkeeping</h3>\n                    <p>Accurate and organized financial records.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-calculator\"></i>\n                    <h3>Tax Preparation</h3>\n                    <p>Expert guidance to minimize tax liabilities.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-dollar-sign\"></i>\n                    <h3>Financial Planning</h3>\n                    <p>Strategic advice for long-term growth.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-file-invoice-dollar\"></i>\n                    <h3>Payroll Services</h3>\n                    <p>Efficient and compliant payroll management.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"about\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2 class=\"section-title\">About Us</h2>\n            <p style=\"text-align: center; max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto;\">At Apex Accounting Solutions, we are dedicated to providing exceptional accounting services with integrity and expertise. Our team of experienced professionals is committed to understanding your unique needs and delivering tailored solutions that drive success. We believe in building strong, long-lasting relationships with our clients, grounded in trust and clear communication.</p>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"contact\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2 class=\"section-title\">Get In Touch</h2>\n            <p>Let's discuss how we can support your financial goals.</p>\n            <div class=\"contact-form\">\n                <form id=\"contactForm\">\n                    <input type=\"text\" id=\"name\" name=\"name\" placeholder=\"Your Name\" required>\n                    <input type=\"email\" id=\"email\" name=\"email\" placeholder=\"Your Email\" required>\n                    <textarea id=\"message\" name=\"message\" placeholder=\"Your Message\" required></textarea>\n                    <button type=\"submit\">Send Message</button>\n                </form>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <p>&copy; 2023 Apex Accounting Solutions. All rights reserved.</p>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        document.getElementById('contactForm').addEventListener('submit', function(event) {\n            event.preventDefault();\n            alert('Thank you for your message! We will be in touch soon.');\n            this.reset();\n        });\n    </script>\n</body>\n</html>\n"}